-- Nearly Half of Colombians Disapprove of Santos, Tiempo Reports
-- B y   R a n d a l l   W o o d s
-- 2012-08-05T17:42:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-05/nearly-half-of-colombians-disapprove-of-santos-tiempo-reports.html
President  Juan Manuel Santos  received
a 49.7 percent disapproval rating on the manner in which he’s
governing, while 43.9 percent of Colombians gave him an approval
rating, according to a poll by Datexco Co.  published today  in El
Tiempo newspaper’s online edition.  The poll also found 67.4 percent don’t support Santos’s re-
election.  The July 30 to Aug. 1 survey of 1,200 people has a margin
of error of plus or minus 2.83 percentage points, the Bogota-
based newspaper said, without providing comparative data from
previous polls.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Randall Woods in Santiago at 
